title: DAZ3D - Poser - Anubis for Genesis and G2M
description:
Anubis for Genesis
------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/dde8212c7386bf0408211072e02dc9d6.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/12728

Experience the power of Genesis with one of the first characters constructed and designed for the new platform. Meet Anubis. Regal, Egyptian, canid, and flexible. Anubis will stand guard over the dead, undead, or soon to be dead, or however your imagination sees fit. Anubis comes ready to render with Egyptian style clothing, including arm bands, head piece, loin cloth, and neck collar. Each item included contains its own texture set. Experiment, create, be free and show us what you can do with Anubis.


Anubis for Genesis 2 Male
-------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/1cb2f13bec395add6cd1ffb6b6066695.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/20754

The Egyptian God Anubis has been brought to life again. This version is for Genesis 2 Male with 9 material presets which includes a tattoo version. There are 10 great action poses to get you started and conforming codpiece, custom JCMs to give smoother bends and several facial expressions supported as well. Full Poser DSON support and custom poser materials. Check out for the Genesis 2 Female Anubis as they make an excellent couple! This is a great add-on for your fantasy scenes
